SUMMARY:Code to cloud: Fast-track delivery with GitHub Copilot and Azure
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nSee how to build\, test\, and deplo
 y cloud apps faster with GitHub Copilot and Azure. In this session\, you
 ’ll get real-world demos that show how Copilot’s AI agents automate pl
 anning\, coding\, and deployment. Azure’s built-in tools help you catch 
 issues before they reach production.\n\nCut manual work\, speed up release
 s\, and improve reliability with AI-driven workflows from your first commi
 t to live operations. Leave ready to deliver better software with less str
 ess and more confidence.\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! [Lear
 n more here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1625/?wt.mc_
 id=meetup_S-1625_webpage_reactor)
